Typically used by the [[Gand/Legends|Gand]], '''ammonia bombs''' were explosives that, when thrown or detonated,<ref name="NEGtWaT">''[[The New Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref> distributed a large amount of [[Ammonia/Legends|ammonia]] into the [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]] of [[Oxygen/Legends|oxygen]]-rich [[Planet/Legends|worlds]].<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|II|29|ammonia bombs}}</ref> They were thus lethal to most oxygen-breathers and many [[Species/Legends|species]] would not utilize these weapons. However, since many Gand races were [[Breather Gand|ammonia-breathers]], Gand [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] would use ammonia [[Bomb/Legends|bombs]] if necessary.<ref name="NEGtWaT" /> [[Zuckuss/Legends|Zuckuss]], one such Gand bounty hunter, was notable for his usage of ammonia bombs, which he would often hide up his sleeves.<ref name="OPF">{{StoryCite|story=Of Possible Futures: The Tale of Zuckuss and 4-LOM|book=Tales of the Bounty Hunters}}</ref>

